blog.name: oxymitch
blog.title: Whatever Mitch
blog.description:
I am Mitch of Singapore, also an Ace. I enjoy reading superhero comics (especially Marvel); comic books aren't just for boys, girls read it too. However, I have no interest in any Marvel movie due to my jaded attitude, so I prefer Marvel cartoons like 90s X-Men TAS and Avengers EMH. 
Those Marvel comics I love reading are New Warriors, X-Men, Young Avengers, X-Factor, Avengers (not that Bendis era), Generation X, Avengers Academy and X-Force. 
Big fan of New Warriors and X-Men. 
My Favourite Marvel characters are...GAMBIT (Remy LeBeau), JUBILEE (Jubilation Lee), SPEEDBALL (Robbie Baldwin), WICCAN (Billy Kaplan), JUSTICE (Vance Astrovik), ROGUE (Anna Marie), SPEED (Tommy Shepherd), NIGHTCRAWLER (Kurt Wagner), FIRESTAR (Angelica Jones), QUICKSILVER (Pietro Maximoff), SHE-HULK (Jennifer Walters), QUASAR (Wendell Vaughn) and COSMO the space dog.

summary: “Y/n hang on I’m coming.” Peter said into the phone attempting to hide the desperation in his voice.   “I know.” She replied...
body:
“Y/n hang on I’m coming.” Peter said into the phone attempting to hide the desperation in his voice. 

“I know.” She replied sadly, biting her lip. “But he’ll kill you if you do.”

“I’ll be careful.” Peter promised leaning his head back against the locker. “But no matter what happens, just know you’re worth it and I love you.” He said swallowing the lump in his throat. 

“I love you too.” She whispered back as the tears finally spilled from her eyes.

“I’m so sorry.” Peter said closing his eyes. 

“You’ll be real sorry if you don’t get here in the next fifteen minutes.” Y/n’s kidnapper growled into the phone. “Tick tock Spider.” Was the last thing Peter heard before the line went dead. 

He shoved his phone into his pocket as he took off down the school hallway as fast as he could, removing his tie in the process. He was going to save his girlfriend if it was the last thing he did.
